data.meta_description:
Visiting COMRAT, the capital city of GAGAUZIA, an autonomous territorial unit of Moldova.
	
	Walking through the city included:
	- Central Park
	- Lenin Statue
	- Tank Memorial 
	- Trying Kvas, a very famous local drink from soviet times
	- Comrat Regional History Museum 
	- Comrat State University 
	
	Moldova  July 2022 #itravelanddance
data.text:
Visiting COMRAT, the capital city of GAGAUZIA, an autonomous territorial unit of Moldova.

Walking through the city included:

- Central Park

- Lenin Statue

- Tank Memorial

- Trying Kvas, a very famous local drink from soviet times

- Comrat Regional History Museum

- Comrat State University

Moldova July 2022 #itravelanddance
